    ('Sissi - Schicksalsjahre einer Kaiserin', 'After a wonderful time in Hungary Sissi falls extremely ill and must retreat to a Mediterranean climate to rest. The young empress’ mother takes her from Austria to recover in Madeira.', '/kfdkl2YbZdsgnnlcJ5MHYyddR0E.jpg', 1957),
