    ('Teen Titans: The Judas Contract', 'Tara Markov is a girl who has power over earth and stone; she is also more than she seems. Is the newest Teen Titan an ally or a threat? And what are the mercenary Deathstroke''s plans for the Titans?', '/ut5F7z1U89zKz9GZAtbJHF7ljqV.jpg', 2017),
