    ('The Baker', 'Milo (Damian Lewis) is a professional hit man living on the edge. When failing to fulfil a contract for the first time, Milo escapes the city to avoid the wrath of his employers. Hiding out in a remote rural village, the locals mistake him for the new baker.', '/5aFFRVjCeqO9xnlyf3Si9vTVofI.jpg', 2007),
