    ('It Comes at Night', 'Secure within a desolate home as an unnatural threat terrorizes the world, a man has established a tenuous domestic order with his wife and son, but this will soon be put to test when a desperate young family arrives seeking refuge.', '/h9VOirT4dKXzVyVzZZxPfAghmRV.jpg', 2017),
    ('Megan Leavey', 'The true story of Marine Corporal Megan Leavey, who forms a powerful bond with an aggressive combat dog, Rex. While deployed in Iraq, the two complete more than 100 missions and save countless lives, until an IED explosion puts their faithfulness to the test.', '/yq66hYkXFaj2DDqCkF6T2wT7VxQ.jpg', 2017),
    ('My Cousin Rachel', 'A young Englishman plots revenge against his mysterious, beautiful cousin, believing that she murdered his guardian. But his feelings become complicated as he finds himself falling under the beguiling spell of her charms.', '/yz9Pnx5tbpZOHWsCD0LtoTCgmLi.jpg', 2017),
    ('Cars 3', 'Blindsided by a new generation of blazing-fast racers, the legendary Lightning McQueen is suddenly pushed out of the sport he loves. To get back in the game, he will need the help of an eager young race technician with her own plan to win, inspiration from the late Fabulous Hudson Hornet, and a few unexpected turns. Proving that #95 isn''t through yet will test the heart of a champion on Piston Cup Racing’s biggest stage!', '/fyy1nDC8wm553FCiBDojkJmKLCs.jpg', 2017),
    ('バイオハザード ヴェンデッタ', 'BSAA Chris Redfield enlists the help of government agent Leon S. Kennedy and Professor Rebecca Chambers from Alexander Institute of Biotechnology to stop a death merchant with a vengeance from spreading a deadly virus in New York.', '/88qfHWhlOBYXp69277QFhdPYnWf.jpg', 2017),
    ('Boyka: Undisputed IV', 'In the fourth installment of the fighting franchise, Boyka is shooting for the big leagues when an accidental death in the ring makes him question everything he stands for. When he finds out the wife of the man he accidentally killed is in trouble, Boyka offers to fight in a series of impossible battles to free her from a life of servitude', '/mWiqc87iTs1qujxm2Q0NRzGvWSN.jpg', 2016),
    ('The Book of Henry', 'Naomi Watts stars as Susan, a single mother of two, working as a waitress in a small town. Her son, Henry, is an 11-year-old genius who not only manages the family finances but acts as emotional support for his mother and younger brother. When Henry discovers that the girl next door has a terrible secret, he implores Susan to take matters into her own hands in this imaginative and emotional drama.', '/suLFg4UjvM5BoDipg2Wu3gZ802T.jpg', 2017),
    ('Une vraie jeune fille', 'Bored and restless, Alice spends much of her time lusting after Jim, a local sawmill worker. When not lusting after him, Alice fills the hours with such pursuits as writing her name on a mirror with vaginal secretions and wandering the fields with her underwear around her ankles. And, in true teenaged tradition, she spends a lot of time writing in her diary.', '/vmUxfIYlVzPBKIEvRcmqPzU6lB.jpg', 1976),
    ('The Wall', 'An American sniper and his spotter engage in a deadly cat-and-mouse game with an Iraqi sniper.', '/8POAZwZpp24l1IgKKM8ZRAQ2kid.jpg', 2017),
    ('Phoenix Forgotten', '20 years after three teenagers disappeared in the wake of mysterious lights appearing above Phoenix, Arizona, unseen footage from that night has been discovered, chronicling the final hours of their fateful expedition.', '/8GJ9a0FgkCKIqKvGtkppTTALGG3.jpg', 2017),
