    ('The Hunter''s Prayer', 'An assassin helps a young woman avenge the death of her family.', '/2qVnSDniGtf2mL941v2izSIzpon.jpg', 2017),
    ('Casper: A Spirited Beginning', 'A prequel to the first animated/live-action Casper feature, Casper: A Spirited Beginning introduces the friendliest ghost you''ll ever know and explains how Casper met and befriended the other ghouls at Applegate Manor. After being stranded, Casper meets young Chris Carson, a lonely kid who decides to teach Casper how to be a proper ghost', '/wiqN1ecTBEFbOZPdM77wrpAVQbY.jpg', 1997),
